<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><head><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml><x:ExcelWorkbook><x:ExcelWorksheets><x:ExcelWorksheet><x:Name>Worksheet</x:Name><x:WorksheetOptions><x:DisplayGridlines/></x:WorksheetOptions></x:ExcelWorksheet></x:ExcelWorksheets></x:ExcelWorkbook></xml><![endif]--></head><body><table>   <thead> <tr class="over_header"> <th aria-label=" " data-stat="header_empty_0" colspan="16" class=" poptip over_header center" style="left: -520px; position: sticky; text-align: right; z-index: 20; border-right: 1px solid rgb(148, 150, 152);"></th> <th aria-label="Passing" data-stat="header_pass" colspan="19" class="poptip over_header center not_sticky">Passing</th> <th aria-label="Rushing" data-stat="header_rush" colspan="6" class="poptip over_header center not_sticky">Rushing</th> <th aria-label="Receiving" data-stat="header_rec" colspan="9" class="poptip over_header center not_sticky">Receiving</th> <th aria-label="Fantasy" data-stat="header_fantasy" colspan="4" class="poptip over_header center not_sticky">Fantasy</th> <th class="not_sticky"></th> </tr> <tr> <th aria-label="Rk" data-stat="ranker" scope="col" class="ranker poptip center" data-tip="Rank">Rk</th> <th aria-label="Player" data-stat="name_display" scope="col" class=" poptip sort_default_asc center">Player</th> <th aria-label="Yds" data-stat="pass_yds" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Yards Gained by Passing&lt;br&gt;For teams, sack yardage is deducted from this total">Yds</th> <th aria-label="TD" data-stat="pass_td" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passing Touchdowns">TD</th> <th aria-label="Yds" data-stat="rush_yds" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Rushing Yards Gained (sack yardage is not included by NFL)">Yds</th> <th aria-label="FantPt" data-stat="fantasy_points" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Fantasy points:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 1 point per 25 yards passing&lt;br /&gt; 4 points per passing touchdown&lt;br /&gt; -2 points per interception thrown&lt;br /&gt; 1 point per 10 yards rushing/receiving&lt;br /&gt; 6 points per TD&lt;br /&gt; 2 points per two-point conversion&lt;br /&gt; -2 points per fumble lost (est. prior to 1994)" data-filter="1" data-name="">FantPt</th> <th aria-label="Yds" data-stat="rec_yds" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Receiving Yards">Yds</th> <th aria-label="Day" data-stat="game_day_of_week" scope="col" class=" poptip left">Day</th> <th aria-label="G#" data-stat="game_num" scope="col" class=" poptip right" data-tip="Game number of team">G#</th> <th aria-label="Week" data-stat="week_num" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Week number in season">Week</th> <th aria-label="Date" data-stat="date" scope="col" class=" poptip sort_col center">Date</th> <th aria-label="Age" data-stat="age_on_day" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="As of the date of the game listed. Age is Years-Days.">Age</th> <th aria-label="Team" data-stat="team_name_abbr" scope="col" class=" poptip sort_default_asc center">Team</th> <th aria-label=" " data-stat="game_location" scope="col" class=" poptip center"></th> <th aria-label="Opp" data-stat="opp_name_abbr" scope="col" class=" poptip sort_default_asc center">Opp</th> <th aria-label="Result" data-stat="game_result" scope="col" class=" poptip center">Result</th> <th aria-label="Cmp" data-stat="pass_cmp" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passes completed">Cmp</th> <th aria-label="Att" data-stat="pass_att" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passes attempted">Att</th> <th aria-label="Inc" data-stat="pass_inc" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passes incomplete (attempts-completions)">Inc</th> <th aria-label="Cmp%" data-stat="pass_cmp_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Percentage of Passes Completed&lt;br&gt;Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." data-filter="1" data-name="">Cmp%</th> <th aria-label="Yds" data-stat="pass_yds" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Yards Gained by Passing&lt;br&gt;For teams, sack yardage is deducted from this total">Yds</th> <th aria-label="TD" data-stat="pass_td" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Passing Touchdowns">TD</th> <th aria-label="Int" data-stat="pass_int" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Interceptions thrown">Int</th> <th aria-label="Pick6" data-stat="pass_int_td" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Interceptions thrown by this quarterback and returned for a touchdown (since 1950)">Pick6</th> <th aria-label="TD%" data-stat="pass_td_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Percentage of Touchdowns Thrown when Attempting to Pass &lt;br&gt;Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader" data-filter="1" data-name="">TD%</th> <th aria-label="Int%" data-stat="pass_int_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Percentage of Times Intercepted when Attempting to Pass &lt;br&gt;Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader.&lt;br /&gt;" data-filter="1" data-name="">Int%</th> <th aria-label="Rate" data-stat="pass_rating" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Passer Rating, &lt;a href='https://www.pro-football-reference.com/about/glossary.htm'&gt;see glossary&lt;/a&gt; for details&lt;br&gt;Different ratings are used by the NFL and NCAA.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader, minimum 150 pass attempts for playoffs leader." data-filter="1" data-name="">Rate</th> <th aria-label="Sk" data-stat="pass_sacked" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Times sacked (first recorded in 1969, player per game since 1981)">Sk</th> <th aria-label="Yds" data-stat="pass_sacked_yds" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Yards lost due to sacks (first recorded in 1969, player per game since 1981)">Yds</th> <th aria-label="Sk%" data-stat="pass_sacked_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Percentage of Time Sacked when Attempting to Pass: Times Sacked / (Passes Attempted + Times Sacked)&lt;br&gt;Minimum 14 attempts + sacks per scheduled game to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader" data-filter="1" data-name="">Sk%</th> <th aria-label="Y/A" data-stat="pass_yds_per_att" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Yards gained per pass attempt &lt;br&gt;Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.&lt;br&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." data-filter="1" data-name="">Y/A</th> <th aria-label="AY/A" data-stat="pass_adj_yds_per_att" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Adjusted Yards gained per pass attempt&lt;br /&gt;(Passing Yards + 20 * Passing TD - 45 * Interceptions) / (Passes Attempted)&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." data-filter="1" data-name="">AY/A</th> <th aria-label="ANY/A" data-stat="pass_adj_net_yds_per_att" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;b&gt;Adjusted Net Yards per Pass Attempt&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;(Passing Yards - Sack Yards + (20 * Passing TD) - (45 * Interceptions)) / (Passes Attempted + Times Sacked)&lt;br&gt;Minimum 14 attempts per scheduled game to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader." data-filter="1" data-name="">ANY/A</th> <th aria-label="Y/C" data-stat="pass_yds_per_cmp" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="&lt;b&gt;Yards gained per pass completion&lt;/b&gt; (Passing Yards) / (Passes Completed)&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 14 pass attempts per schedule game to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 1500 pass attempts to qualify as career leader" data-filter="1" data-name="">Y/C</th> <th aria-label="Succ%" data-stat="pass_success" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Passing Success Rate&lt;br /&gt;A successful pass gains at least 40% of yards required on 1st down, 60% of yards required on 2nd down, and 100% on 3rd or 4th down. Denominator is pass attempts + times sacked." data-filter="1" data-name="">Succ%</th> <th aria-label="Att" data-stat="rush_att" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Rushing Attempts (sacks not included in NFL)">Att</th> <th aria-label="Yds" data-stat="rush_yds" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Rushing Yards Gained (sack yardage is not included by NFL)">Yds</th> <th aria-label="Y/A" data-stat="rush_yds_per_att" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Rushing Yards per Attempt&lt;br&gt;Minimum 6.25 rushes per game scheduled to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 750 rushes to qualify as career leader." data-filter="1" data-name="">Y/A</th> <th aria-label="TD" data-stat="rush_td" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Rushing Touchdowns">TD</th> <th aria-label="1D" data-stat="rush_first_down" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="First downs rushing">1D</th> <th aria-label="Succ%" data-stat="rush_success" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Rushing Success Rate&lt;br /&gt;A successful rush gains least 40% of yards required on 1st down, 60% of yards required on 2nd down, and 100% on 3rd or 4th down. Denominator is rushing attempts." data-filter="1" data-name="">Succ%</th> <th aria-label="Tgt" data-stat="targets" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Pass Targets (since 1978, derived from NFL play-by-play data)">Tgt</th> <th aria-label="Rec" data-stat="rec" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Receptions">Rec</th> <th aria-label="Yds" data-stat="rec_yds" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Receiving Yards">Yds</th> <th aria-label="Y/R" data-stat="rec_yds_per_rec" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Receiving Yards per Reception&lt;br&gt;Minimum 1.875 catches per game scheduled to qualify as leader.&lt;br /&gt;Minimum 200 receptions to qualify as career leader." data-filter="1" data-name="">Y/R</th> <th aria-label="TD" data-stat="rec_td" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="Receiving Touchdowns">TD</th> <th aria-label="Ctch%" data-stat="catch_pct" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Catch%, receptions divided by targets (since 1978)" data-filter="1" data-name="">Ctch%</th> <th aria-label="Y/Tgt" data-stat="rec_yds_per_tgt" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Receiving Yards per Target (target numbers since 1978)" data-filter="1" data-name="">Y/Tgt</th> <th aria-label="1D" data-stat="rec_first_down" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="First downs receiving">1D</th> <th aria-label="Succ%" data-stat="rec_success" scope="col" class=" poptip hide_non_quals center" data-tip="Receiving Success Rate&lt;br /&gt;A successful reception gains at least 40% of yards required on 1st down, 60% of yards required on 2nd down, and 100% on 3rd or 4th down. Denominator is targets." data-filter="1" data-name="">Succ%</th> <th aria-label="FantPt" data-stat="fantasy_points" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Fantasy points:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 1 point per 25 yards passing&lt;br /&gt; 4 points per passing touchdown&lt;br /&gt; -2 points per interception thrown&lt;br /&gt; 1 point per 10 yards rushing/receiving&lt;br /&gt; 6 points per TD&lt;br /&gt; 2 points per two-point conversion&lt;br /&gt; -2 points per fumble lost (est. prior to 1994)" data-filter="1" data-name="">FantPt</th> <th aria-label="PPR" data-stat="fantasy_points_ppr" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Fantasy points (PPR scoring):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; 1 point per 25 yards passing&lt;br /&gt; 4 points per passing touchdown&lt;br /&gt; -2 points per interception thrown&lt;br /&gt; 1 point per reception&lt;br /&gt; 1 point per 10 yards rushing/receiving&lt;br /&gt; 6 points per TD&lt;br /&gt; 2 points per two-point conversion&lt;br /&gt; -2 points per fumble lost (est. prior to 1994)" data-filter="1" data-name="">PPR</th> <th aria-label="DKPt" data-stat="draftkings_points" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Fantasy points (DraftKings scoring)&lt;/strong&gt;" data-filter="1" data-name="">DKPt</th> <th aria-label="FDPt" data-stat="fanduel_points" scope="col" class=" poptip center" data-tip="&lt;strong&gt;Fantasy points (FanDuel scoring)&lt;/strong&gt;" data-filter="1" data-name="">FDPt</th> <th aria-label="Pos." data-stat="pos_game" scope="col" class=" poptip center">Pos.</th> </tr> </thead> <tbody><tr data-row="0"> <th scope="row" class="right " data-stat="ranker" csk="1401">1401</th> <td class="left " data-append-csv="HeywDa00" data-stat="name_display" csk="Heyward-Bey Darrius">Darrius Heyward-Bey</td> <td class="right iz" data-stat="pass_yds">0</td> <td class="right iz" data-stat="pass_td">0</td> <td class="right iz" data-stat="rush_yds">0</td> <td class="right " data-stat="fantasy_points" csk="0.20">0.20</td> <td class="right " data-stat="rec_yds">2</td> <td class="left " data-stat="game_day_of_week">Sun</td> <td class="right " data-stat="game_num">4</td> <td class="right " data-stat="week_num">4</td> <td class="left " data-stat="date">2010-10-03</td> <td class="right " data-stat="age_on_day">23-219</td> <td class="left " data-stat="team_name_abbr">OAK</td> <td class="center " data-stat="game_location"></td> <td class="left " data-stat="opp_name_abbr">HOU</td> <td class="left " data-stat="game_result" csk="-6.7600000000">L, 24-31</td> <td class="right iz" data-stat="pass_cmp">0</td> <td class="right iz" data-stat="pass_att">0</td> <td class="right